#: templates/main/help.html:11
msgid "Easily add information about images on Wikimedia Commons"
msgstr "Cuir faisnéis faoi íomhánna ar Wikimedia Commons go héasca"

#: templates/main/help.html:16
#, python-format
msgid "<strong>ISA</strong> is a fun, multilingual, mobile-first tool, that makes it easy for people to add \"micro contributions\" in the form of <a %(link_attrs)s>structured data</a> to images on Wikimedia Commons that have been added by Wiki Loves competitions."
msgstr "Is uirlis spraíúil, ilteangach, atá dírithe ar fhóin phóca í <strong>ISA</strong>, a fhágann go bhfuil sé éasca do dhaoine \"micrea-ranníocaíochtaí\" i bhfoirm <a %(link_attrs)s>sonraí struchtúrtha</a> a chur le híomhánna ar Wikimedia Commons atá curtha leis ag comórtais Wiki Loves."

#: templates/main/help.html:19
#, python-format
msgid "ISA is originally built to provide better multilingual and structured descriptions of <a %(link_attrs)s>Wiki Loves Africa</a> images."
msgstr "Tógadh ISA ar dtús chun cur síos ilteangach agus struchtúrtha níos fearr a sholáthar ar íomhánna <a %(link_attrs)s>Wiki Loves Africa</a>."

#: templates/main/help.html:20
msgid "But it is also developed to be useful to all of the <a link_attrs>Wiki Loves competitions</a> and, ultimately, for <strong>all media files</strong> on Wikimedia Commons."
msgstr "Ach tá sé forbartha freisin le bheith úsáideach do gach ceann de na <a link_attrs>comórtais Wiki Loves</a> agus, sa deireadh, do <strong>gach comhad meán</strong> ar Wikimedia Commons."

#: templates/main/help.html:23
msgid "What is Wikimedia Commons?"
msgstr "Cad é Wikimedia Commons?"

#: templates/main/help.html:26
msgid "<strong>Wikimedia Commons</strong> (also known as \"Commons\") is a Wikimedia project, a sister project of Wikipedia. It hosts a collection of millions of freely usable media files to which anyone can contribute."
msgstr "Is tionscadal Wikimedia é <strong>Wikimedia Commons</strong> (ar a dtugtar \"Commons\" freisin), tionscadal deirfiúr de chuid Vicipéid. Tá bailiúchán de na milliúin comhad meán inúsáidte go saor ann ar féidir le duine ar bith cur leo."

#: templates/main/help.html:27
msgid "All the freely licensed photos, audio and video files, PDFs and other media on Wikipedia are stored on Commons."
msgstr "Tá na grianghraif, na comhaid fuaime agus físe, na PDFanna agus na meáin eile go léir atá ceadúnaithe go saor ar Vicipéid stóráilte ar Commons."

#: templates/main/help.html:30
msgid "Wikimedia Commons grows rapidly, by approximately 5 million new media files per year."
msgstr "Fásann Wikimedia Commons go tapa, thart ar 5 mhilliún comhad meán nua in aghaidh na bliana."

#: templates/main/help.html:33
msgid "Thousands of volunteers upload files to Commons, and integrate these into Wikimedia projects, like Wikipedia, to illustrate the content there and to share that media with the public."
msgstr "Uaslódálann na mílte oibrithe deonacha comhaid chuig Commons, agus comhtháthaíonn siad iad seo i dtionscadail Wikimedia, cosúil le Vicipéid, chun an t-ábhar ann a léiriú agus na meáin sin a roinnt leis an bpobal."

#: templates/main/help.html:34
msgid "Media files on Commons are typically:"
msgstr "Is iad na comhaid meán ar Commons de ghnáth:"

#: templates/main/help.html:37
msgid "Personal photography and media uploaded by individuals, sometimes during Wiki Loves competitions such as Wiki Loves Africa, Wiki Loves Monuments, Wiki Loves Earth etc;"
msgstr "Grianghrafadóireacht phearsanta agus meáin a uaslódáileann daoine aonair, uaireanta le linn comórtais Wiki Loves ar nós Wiki Loves Africa, Wiki Loves Monuments, Wiki Loves Earth etc.;"

#: templates/main/help.html:38
msgid "Freely licensed media files from external websites like Flickr, YouTube, open access journals, and other repositories; and"
msgstr "Comhaid meán ceadúnaithe saor ó shuíomhanna gréasáin sheachtracha ar nós Flickr, YouTube, irisí rochtana oscailte, agus stórtha eile; agus"

#: templates/main/help.html:39
msgid "Donations from institutions and organizations with substantial media collections, large and small, ranging from UNESCO, NASA and the British Library to small local cultural institutions."
msgstr "Síntiúis ó institiúidí agus eagraíochtaí a bhfuil bailiúcháin shuntasacha meán acu, mór agus beag, ó UNESCO, NASA agus Leabharlann na Breataine go hinstitiúidí cultúrtha beaga áitiúla."

#: templates/main/help.html:42
msgid "What is structured data on Commons ?"
msgstr "Cad is sonraí struchtúrtha ar Commons?"

#: templates/main/help.html:44
msgid "<strong>Structured Data on Commons</strong> is a project that provides the technical infrastructure to complement the wikitext, templates and categories on Wikimedia Commons with structured data."
msgstr "Is tionscadal é <strong>Sonraí Struchtúrtha ar Commons</strong> a sholáthraíonn an bonneagar teicniúil chun an téacs vicí, na teimpléid agus na catagóirí ar Wikimedia Commons a chomhlánú le sonraí struchtúrtha."

#: templates/main/help.html:45
msgid "Structured data is data with a high degree of structured organization."
msgstr "Is sonraí a bhfuil ardleibhéal eagrúcháin struchtúrtha iontu iad sonraí struchtúrtha."

#: templates/main/help.html:46
msgid "With more structure, it becomes easier to reuse data in other Wikimedia projects and by third parties; it also allows computers to process and 'understand' it."
msgstr "Le níos mó struchtúir, bíonn sé níos éasca sonraí a athúsáid i dtionscadail Wikimedia eile agus ag tríú páirtithe; tugann sé deis do ríomhairí iad a phróiseáil agus a 'thuiscint' freisin."

#: templates/main/help.html:49
msgid "Structured Data is an ongoing project that was launched in 2019!.. whilst Wikimedia Commons has been around for years!"
msgstr "Is tionscadal leanúnach é Sonraí Struchtúrtha a seoladh in 2019!... cé go bhfuil Wikimedia Commons ann le blianta!"

#: templates/main/help.html:50
msgid "There are literally millions of pictures hosted on Wikimedia Commons... that need attention and love."
msgstr "Tá na milliúin pictiúr ar Wikimedia Commons... a bhfuil aird agus grá ag teastáil uathu."

#: templates/main/help.html:51
msgid "Millions of pictures that are not described with structured data at the moment."
msgstr "Milliúin pictiúr nach bhfuil cur síos orthu le sonraí struchtúrtha faoi láthair."

#: templates/main/help.html:54
msgid "How are we going to do that?"
msgstr "Conas a dhéanfaimid é sin?"

#: templates/main/help.html:57
msgid "<strong>Curating</strong>, or curation, in the narrow sense, means: selecting and organizing pieces of artwork and cultural heritage for an exhibition."
msgstr "Ciallaíonn <strong>ag coimeád</strong>, nó coimeád, sa chiall chúng: píosaí ealaíne agus oidhreachta cultúrtha a roghnú agus a eagrú le haghaidh taispeántais."

#: templates/main/help.html:58
msgid "This term can also be used more broadly, to describe any activity that involves selecting, organizing and presenting information."
msgstr "Is féidir an téarma seo a úsáid ar bhealach níos leithne freisin, chun cur síos a dhéanamh ar aon ghníomhaíocht a bhaineann le faisnéis a roghnú, a eagrú agus a chur i láthair."

#: templates/main/help.html:59
msgid "In the context of Structured Data on Commons, curating means all the activities performed by Commons contributors to organize and present the media files on Wikimedia Commons: administrative actions, adding more and better metadata to the files, grouping them in categories, creating galleries..."
msgstr "I gcomhthéacs Sonraí Struchtúrtha ar Commons, ciallaíonn coimeád na gníomhaíochtaí uile a dhéanann rannpháirtithe Commons chun na comhaid meán ar Wikimedia Commons a eagrú agus a chur i láthair: gníomhartha riaracháin, meiteashonraí níos mó agus níos fearr a chur leis na comhaid, iad a ghrúpáil i gcatagóirí, gailearaithe a chruthú..."

#: templates/main/help.html:62
msgid "So... how does the ISA tool fit in there?"
msgstr "Mar sin... conas a oireann an uirlis ISA ansin?"

#: templates/main/help.html:65
msgid "The ISA tool allows to add two different types of structured data to set of pictures: captions and depicts (more explanations below on what captions and depicts are)."
msgstr "Leis an uirlis ISA is féidir dhá chineál sonraí struchtúrtha a chur le sraith pictiúr: fotheidil agus léirithe (tuilleadh mínithe thíos ar cad is fotheidil agus léirithe ann)."

#: templates/main/help.html:66
msgid "It is a multilingual, mobile-first 'micro-contributions' tool, that makes it easy for people to add structured data to images contributed to Wiki Loves competitions on Wikimedia Commons."
msgstr "Is uirlis ilteangach, soghluaiste-chéadfach í 'micrea-ranníocaíochtaí', a fhágann go bhfuil sé éasca do dhaoine sonraí struchtúrtha a chur le híomhánna a chuirtear ar fáil do chomórtais Wiki Loves ar Wikimedia Commons."

#: templates/main/help.html:69
msgid "The tool operates with curated campaigns created by coordinators."
msgstr "Oibríonn an uirlis le feachtais choimeádta arna gcruthú ag comhordaitheoirí."

#: templates/main/help.html:70
msgid "Anyone with a Wikimedia account may be a coordinator!"
msgstr "Féadfaidh aon duine a bhfuil cuntas Wikimedia aige a bheith ina chomhordaitheoir!"

#: templates/main/help.html:73
msgid "With ISA, the coordinator can choose a predefined set of images on Commons, select a starting date and an end date for the campaign, and provide general information about the campaign itself."
msgstr "Le ISA, is féidir leis an gcomhordaitheoir sraith íomhánna réamhshainithe a roghnú ar Commons, dáta tosaigh agus dáta deiridh a roghnú don fheachtas, agus faisnéis ghinearálta a sholáthar faoin bhfeachtas féin."

#: templates/main/help.html:74
msgid "The coordinator can then ask contributors to \"tag\" these images with multilingual structured metadata (depicts and/or captions)."
msgstr "Ansin, féadfaidh an comhordaitheoir iarraidh ar rannpháirtithe na híomhánna seo a \"chlibeáil\" le meiteashonraí struchtúrtha ilteangacha (léirithe agus/nó fotheidil)."

#: templates/main/help.html:75
msgid "Points are counted for each contribution made by a participant, and therefore it is possible to organize \"tagging\" or micro-contributions competitions or challenges with ISA."
msgstr "Déantar pointí a chomhaireamh as gach ranníocaíocht a dhéanann rannpháirtí, agus dá bhrí sin is féidir comórtais nó dúshláin \"clibeála\" nó micrea-ranníocaíochtaí a eagrú le ISA."

#: templates/main/help.html:78
msgid "Anyone with a Wikimedia account can contribute to add structured metadata to a campaign."
msgstr "Is féidir le duine ar bith a bhfuil cuntas Wikimedia aige cur le meiteashonraí struchtúrtha a chur le feachtas."

#: templates/main/help.html:79
msgid "The only requirement is... to be logged-in."
msgstr "Is é an t-aon riachtanas ná... a bheith logáilte isteach."

#: templates/main/help.html:82
msgid "Learn more about file captions and depicts"
msgstr "Foghlaim tuilleadh faoi fhotheidil agus léirithe comhad"

#: templates/main/help.html:85
msgid "File captions are a feature part of Structured data."
msgstr "Is cuid ghné de shonraí struchtúrtha iad fotheidil chomhad."

#: templates/main/help.html:86
msgid "They are meant to store short, multilingual description about files."
msgstr "Tá siad ceaptha chun cur síos gearr, ilteangach faoi chomhaid a stóráil."

#: templates/main/help.html:89
msgid "What is a good caption ? and what is the difference between our good old file descriptions and captions ?"
msgstr "Cad is fotheideal maith ann? agus cad é an difríocht idir ár seanthuairiscí maithe ar chomhaid agus ár bhfotheidil?"

#: templates/main/help.html:92
msgid "First, captions are meant to be simple and short."
msgstr "Ar dtús, tá fotheidil ceaptha a bheith simplí agus gearr."

#: templates/main/help.html:93
msgid "While descriptions can be very expansive, captions are limited to 255 characters in length, and cannot contain markup (like Wikitext links or HTML) and do not support external links."
msgstr "Cé gur féidir le tuairiscí a bheith an-fhada, tá teorainn 255 carachtar ar fhad le fotheidil, agus ní féidir leo marcáil a bheith iontu (cosúil le naisc Wikitext nó HTML) agus ní thacaíonn siad le naisc sheachtracha."

#: templates/main/help.html:96
msgid "In many cases, the caption will be similar or identical to the description."
msgstr "I go leor cásanna, beidh an fotheideal cosúil nó comhionann leis an tuairisc."

#: templates/main/help.html:97
msgid "But in other cases, there is a very extensive description (858 characters, and links) and the caption is much shorter (more or less the same caption used on the Wikipedia articles using that image)."
msgstr "Ach i gcásanna eile, bíonn cur síos an-fhairsing ann (858 carachtar, agus naisc) agus bíonn an fotheideal i bhfad níos giorra (an fotheideal céanna a úsáidtear ar na hairteagail Vicipéide a úsáideann an íomhá sin)."

#: templates/main/help.html:100
msgid "Only text which is so short that it is not copyrightable should be copied into captions, as captions are published under a CC0 (\"public domain\") waiver."
msgstr "Níor cheart ach téacs atá chomh gearr sin nach bhfuil cóipcheart air a chóipeáil isteach i bhfotheidil, toisc go bhfoilsítear fotheidil faoi tharscaoileadh CC0 (\"fearann ​​poiblí\")."

#: templates/main/help.html:103
msgid "One of the core benefits of captions is improved language-aware searchability."
msgstr "Ceann de na príomhbhuntáistí a bhaineann le fotheidil ná inchuardach feabhsaithe atá feasach ar theanga."

#: templates/main/help.html:104
msgid "Classical file descriptions are in the wikitext, and are only searchable through full-text search, which necessarily searches through the entire page contents, including categories and license templates; and it is not possible to do search search per language."
msgstr "Bíonn tuairiscí clasaiceacha ar chomhaid sa vicíthéacs, agus ní féidir iad a chuardach ach trí chuardach téacs iomlán, rud a chuardaíonn ábhar iomlán an leathanaigh, lena n-áirítear catagóirí agus teimpléid cheadúnais; agus ní féidir cuardach a dhéanamh de réir teanga."

#: templates/main/help.html:107
msgid "Captions are available as part of our structured data, while descriptions are not."
msgstr "Tá fotheidil ar fáil mar chuid dár sonraí struchtúrtha, ach níl tuairiscí ar fáil."

#: templates/main/help.html:108
msgid "In technical terms, a description is plain wikitext wrapped in a language template, wrapped again in an Information template; while captions are Wikibase labels."
msgstr "I dtéarmaí teicniúla, is téacs simplí vicí é cur síos atá fillte i dteimpléad teanga, fillte arís i dteimpléad Faisnéise; agus is lipéid Wikibase iad fotheidil."

#: templates/main/help.html:111
msgid "As such, captions will be searchable through the API, making it easy to find/filter/pull captions from files as metadata."
msgstr "Dá bhrí sin, beidh fotheidil inchuardaithe tríd an API, rud a fhágfaidh go mbeidh sé éasca fotheidil a aimsiú/a scagadh/a tharraingt ó chomhaid mar mheiteashonraí."

#: templates/main/help.html:112
msgid "As they are searchable via the API, it is also easier for 3rd party reusers to find and reuse media and the captions themselves."
msgstr "Ós rud é gur féidir iad a chuardach tríd an API, tá sé níos éasca freisin d’athúsáideoirí tríú páirtí meáin agus na fotheidil féin a aimsiú agus a athúsáid."

#: templates/main/help.html:115
msgid "Other possible usages of captions can be:"
msgstr "Is féidir úsáidí eile a bhaint as fotheidil:"

#: templates/main/help.html:118
msgid "filling in infoboxes"
msgstr "ag líonadh boscaí eolais"

#: templates/main/help.html:119
msgid "query files for missing captions in a given language"
msgstr "comhaid fiosrúcháin le haghaidh fotheidil atá ar iarraidh i dteanga ar leith"

#: templates/main/help.html:120
msgid "building lists for translation of important files needing a caption localized for a project or campaign"
msgstr "liostaí a thógáil le haghaidh aistriúcháin comhad tábhachtach a bhfuil fotheideal logánaithe ag teastáil uathu do thionscadal nó do fheachtas"

#: templates/main/help.html:123
msgid "Find more information about Captions here"
msgstr "Faigh tuilleadh eolais faoi Fhotheidil anseo"

#: templates/main/help.html:127
msgid "Depicts is also a feature part of Structured data."
msgstr "Is cuid ghné de shonraí struchtúrtha é Depicts freisin."

#: templates/main/help.html:128
msgid "It was enabled on Wikimedia Commons on April 2019."
msgstr "Cumasaíodh é ar Wikimedia Commons i mí Aibreáin 2019."

#: templates/main/help.html:131
msgid "To add a depicts statement, simply start typing in the search box."
msgstr "Chun ráiteas léiríonn a chur leis, níl le déanamh ach tosú ag clóscríobh sa bhosca cuardaigh."

#: templates/main/help.html:132
msgid "Then for each depicted item in the image, find the appropriate item from Wikidata and select it."
msgstr "Ansin, i gcás gach míre atá léirithe san íomhá, faigh an mhír chuí ó Wikidata agus roghnaigh í."

#: templates/main/help.html:135
msgid "If you have trouble finding the right Wikidata item, test alternative spellings."
msgstr "Má bhíonn deacracht agat an mhír cheart ar Wikidata a aimsiú, déan tástáil ar litriúcháin mhalartacha."

#: templates/main/help.html:138
msgid "If there is no Wikidata item associated with the subject depicted, choose a more generic item which includes your subject as an example."
msgstr "Mura bhfuil aon mhír Wikidata a bhaineann leis an ábhar atá léirithe, roghnaigh mír níos ginearálta a chuimsíonn d’ábhar mar shampla."

#: templates/main/help.html:141
msgid "Be as specific as you can with the primary tag."
msgstr "Bí chomh sonrach agus is féidir leat leis an bpríomhchlib."

#: templates/main/help.html:142
msgid "If there are multiple items clearly and deliberately depicted by the media file, all should be added as separate depicts statements, within reason."
msgstr "Más rud é go bhfuil roinnt míreanna á léiriú go soiléir agus d'aon ghnó sa chomhad meán, ba chóir iad uile a chur leis mar ráitis léirithe ar leithligh, laistigh de réasún."

#: templates/main/help.html:143
msgid "For files that depict dozens or hundreds of items (e.g. movies) only list those items which are most prominent."
msgstr "I gcás comhad a léiríonn dosaenacha nó na céadta mír (e.g. scannáin) ná liostaigh ach na míreanna is suntasaí."

#: templates/main/help.html:146
msgid "There is also an option to mark a particular item as 'prominent'."
msgstr "Tá rogha ann freisin chun mír ar leith a mharcáil mar 'suntasach'."

#: templates/main/help.html:147
msgid "This property refers to the item's prominence in the piece of media."
msgstr "Tagraíonn an airí seo do shuntasacht na míre sa phíosa meán."

#: templates/main/help.html:150
msgid "More information about depicts may be found here :"
msgstr "Is féidir tuilleadh eolais faoi léirithe a fháil anseo:"

#: templates/main/help.html:154
msgid "Using the ISA tool"
msgstr "Ag baint úsáide as an uirlis ISA"

#: templates/main/help.html:157
msgid "More information may be found here:"
msgstr "Is féidir tuilleadh eolais a fháil anseo:"

#: templates/main/help.html:161
msgid "Legal and credits"
msgstr "Dlí agus creidmheasanna"

#: templates/main/help.html:165
msgid "It is running on tools.wmflabs.org, and is subject to the Wikimedia Cloud Services Terms of Use."
msgstr "Tá sé ag rith ar tools.wmflabs.org, agus tá sé faoi réir Théarmaí Úsáide Sheirbhísí Scamall Wikimedia."

#: templates/main/help.html:166
msgid "ISA is published under GPLv3. Content added through the tool to Wikimedia Commons is released under CC0."
msgstr "Tá ISA foilsithe faoi GPLv3. Tá ábhar a chuirtear leis an uirlis chuig Wikimedia Commons eisithe faoi CC0."

#: templates/main/help.html:169
msgid "Image used on the tool :"
msgstr "Íomhá a úsáideadh ar an uirlis:"

#: templates/main/home.html:11
msgid "Easily Add Information about Images on Wikimedia Commons"
msgstr "Cuir Faisnéis faoi Íomhánna ar Wikimedia Commons go Héasca"

#: templates/main/home.html:15
#, python-format
msgid "<strong>ISA</strong> is a multilingual, mobile-first tool, that makes it easy for people to add 'micro-contributions' in the form of <a %(link_attrs)s title='Learn more about structured data'>structured data</a> (descriptions, captions, tags, etc.) to images that have been contributed to Wikimedia Commons by Wiki Loves competitions."
msgstr "Is uirlis ilteangach, atá dírithe ar fhóin phóca, é <strong>ISA</strong> a fhágann go bhfuil sé éasca do dhaoine 'micrea-ranníocaíochtaí' a chur leis i bhfoirm <a %(link_attrs)s title='Learn more about structured data'>sonraí struchtúrtha</a> (tuairiscí, fotheidil, clibeanna, srl.) le híomhánna atá curtha ar fáil do Wikimedia Commons ag comórtais Wiki Loves."

#: templates/main/home.html:16
msgid "<strong>Click on Explore Campaigns to begin!</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Cliceáil ar Iniúchadh Feachtais le tosú!</strong>"

#: templates/main/home.html:19
msgid "Go to the campaign directory to choose a campaign"
msgstr "Téigh chuig an eolaire feachtasaíochta chun feachtas a roghnú"

#: templates/main/home.html:19
msgid "EXPLORE CAMPAIGNS"
msgstr "FEACHTAIS INIÚCHTA"

#: templates/main/home.html:22
msgid "About This Tool"
msgstr "Maidir leis an Uirlis seo"

#: templates/main/home.html:23
msgid "In the long run, the intent behind the tool is to increase the use of the knowledge that is reflected by each image hosted on Wikimedia Commons."
msgstr "San fhadtréimhse, is é an cuspóir atá leis an uirlis ná úsáid an eolais a léirítear i ngach íomhá atá á óstáil ar Wikimedia Commons a mhéadú."

#: templates/main/home.html:24
msgid "The tool is aimed to assist in the usefulness and information of images donated during the Wiki Loves competitions."
msgstr "Tá sé mar aidhm ag an uirlis cabhrú le húsáideacht agus faisnéis na n-íomhánna a bhronntar le linn chomórtais Wiki Loves."

#: templates/main/home.html:25
msgid "It is initially being built to assist in the descriptions of Wiki Loves Africa images, but is being specifically modelled to be useful to all of the Wiki Loves competitions and beyond."
msgstr "Tá sé á thógáil ar dtús chun cabhrú le cur síos a dhéanamh ar íomhánna Wiki Loves Africa, ach tá sé á shamhaltú go sonrach le bheith úsáideach do gach comórtas Wiki Loves agus níos faide anonn."

#: templates/main/home.html:26
msgid "The tool is also designed to be a host of micro contribution competitions proposed by project leaders."
msgstr "Tá an uirlis deartha freisin le bheith ina hóstach ar chomórtais micrea-ranníocaíochtaí arna moladh ag ceannairí tionscadail."

#: templates/main/home.html:27
msgid "ISA is a collaboration between Wiki In Africa, Histropedia and the Structured Data on Commons project."
msgstr "Is comhoibriú idir Wiki In Africa, Histopedia agus an tionscadal Structured Data on Commons é ISA."

#: templates/main/home.html:28
msgid "ISA is not only an acronym for Information Structured Acceleration, but is also a chiShona language word for 'put' or 'place'."
msgstr "Ní hamháin gur acrainm é ISA do Luasghéarú Struchtúrtha Faisnéise, ach is focal i dteanga ChiShona é freisin do 'cuir' nó 'áit'."

